(33, 3, 'joy', 'The Colors of StoBoSa: A Vibrant Artistic Attraction', 'Nestled in La Trinidad, Benguet, Philippines, the Colors of StoBoSa stand as a testament to creativity and community spirit. StoBoSa, derived from the three sitios of Stonehill, Botiwtiw, and Sadjap, is a vibrant mural adorning the landscape along the Halsema Highway.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Community Transformed&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;The StoBoSa Hillside Homes Artwork is not merely a mural; it represents a community&#39;s collective vision and effort to breathe life and color into their surroundings. What was once a cluster of ordinary houses has been transformed into a sprawling canvas bursting with hues and patterns.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Mosaic of Culture and Pride&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Local residents took up brushes and paints to adorn their homes with a kaleidoscope of colors. Geometric shapes mingle with traditional Filipino designs, creating a mosaic that speaks volumes about the community&#39;s heritage and identity. The result is a visual masterpiece that not only enhances the aesthetic appeal of the area but also fosters a sense of pride and unity among its residents.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;The Colors of StoBoSa serve as a reminder of the transformative power of art and community collaboration, turning everyday spaces into vibrant expressions of culture and creativity.', 'travel', 'pic02.jpg', '0000-00-00', 'active'),
(34, 3, 'joy', 'Exploring the Majestic Mayon Volcano and Cagsawa Ruins Park', 'In the heart of Albay, Bicol, lies a scene straight out of a postcard – the breathtaking view of Mayon Volcano from Cagsawa Ruins Park. This iconic sight is not just a picturesque spot but a poignant reminder of the region&#39;s tumultuous past and natural beauty.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Glimpse into History&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Cagsawa Ruins Park stands as a witness to the catastrophic eruption of Mayon Volcano in 1814. What remains of the once-majestic Cagsawa Church is now a hauntingly beautiful ruin, with only the belfry standing tall amidst the remnants. The tragedy that befell the church serves as a stark reminder of the raw power of nature.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;The Perfect Cone of Mayon Volcano&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Mayon Volcano, with its near-perfect conical shape, looms majestically in the backdrop, creating a striking contrast against the historic ruins. This symmetrical beauty of Mayon Volcano has earned it a reputation as one of the most visually stunning volcanoes in the world, attracting visitors from far and wide.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Landscape of Contrasts&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;The juxtaposition of the serene and symmetrical Mayon Volcano with the haunting and historic Cagsawa Ruins paints a vivid and evocative landscape. Photographers seek to capture this mesmerizing scenery, historians delve into the tales of the past, and tourists immerse themselves in the beauty and history that permeate the surroundings.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Visiting Cagsawa Ruins Park offers not just a visual treat but a profound experience that blends nature&#39;s grandeur with the echoes of the past, making it a must-visit destination for travelers seeking both beauty and history in one captivating setting', 'travel', 'mv.jpg', '0000-00-00', 'active'),
(35, 3, 'joy', 'Cheers to youth', '&#13;&#10;Must listen: Cheers to Youth - Seventeen&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;In the symphony of life, there are moments that echo with the raw emotions of youth, capturing the essence of vulnerability, growth, and resilience. The song &#34;Cheers To Youth&#34; resonates with a heartfelt message that speaks to the complexities of self-discovery and the bittersweet journey of coming of age.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Facing Ourselves:&#13;&#10;As the lyrics unfold, we are invited to confront our innermost fears and insecurities, to face ourselves in the mirror of self-reflection. The poignant acknowledgment of self-doubt and the struggle for self-acceptance mirror the universal experience of navigating the uncertainties of youth.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Finding Joy in Small Moments:&#13;&#10;Amidst the chaos and confusion of life, the song reminds us to cherish the simple joys and fleeting moments of happiness. From a brief smile at a small gesture to the warmth of a cozy blanket, &#34;Cheers To Youth&#34; celebrates the beauty of finding solace in the midst of life&#39;s challenges.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Embracing Imperfections:&#13;&#10;The journey of youth is often fraught with self-doubt and the quest for happiness. The song beautifully encapsulates the sentiment of embracing imperfections, acknowledging that each stumble and setback is a part of the journey towards self-discovery and growth.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Toast to Resilience:&#13;&#10;In the face of uncertainty and self-criticism, &#34;Cheers To Youth&#34; offers a toast to resilience and perseverance. It is a reminder that even in moments of vulnerability, there is strength in our voices and the power to sing our truths, wherever we may be on our journey.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;As we navigate the complexities of youth, let us raise a glass to the resilience, vulnerability, and beauty of the human experience. &#34;Cheers To Youth&#34; serves as a poignant reminder that in the tapestry of life, every stumble, every moment of self-reflection, and every small joy contributes to the rich fabric of our existence. Let us embrace the journey, celebrate our imperfections, and find solace in the music that echoes the sentiments of our hearts.', 'music', 'cheersty1.jpg', '0000-00-00', 'active'),
(36, 3, 'joy', 'Headliner', '&#13;&#10;Headliner - Seventeen&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;In the poetic verses of &#34;Headliner,&#34; a serenade to love unfolds, weaving a tapestry of emotions that resonate with the soul. Each lyric, each note, is a melody that dances through the heart, painting a portrait of affection and devotion that transcends time and space.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Embracing Anticipation:&#13;&#10;&#34;Even before I met you, you make my heart flutter,&#34; setting the stage for a tale of yearning and excitement. The anticipation of love, the anticipation of connection, is a delicate dance of emotions that captivates the heart.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Symphony of Longing:&#13;&#10;&#34;I only want to see you, no, I want to show you to everyone,&#34; a declaration of love that knows no bounds. The desire to share love with the world, to bask in the light of affection, fills the air with a symphony of longing and devotion.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Moonlit Serenade:&#13;&#10;&#34;When the sun falls asleep, the moonlight in the morning takes me to you,&#34; a poetic journey guided by the soft glow of the moon. The night becomes a canvas for love&#39;s expression, painting a picture of intimacy and connection under the gentle gaze of the moon.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Harmony of Souls:&#13;&#10;&#34;I&#39;ll sing along to you, the same melody,&#34; a harmonious union of souls that find solace in shared laughter and tears. The night becomes a sanctuary of love, a space where hearts intertwine in a beautiful symphony of emotions.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;The Headliner of Hearts:&#13;&#10;&#34;Because you&#39;re my headliner, my headliner,&#34; a declaration of love that shines brightly in the darkness. The beloved takes center stage in the heart, a beacon of courage and strength that lights the path to countless tomorrows.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;As the echoes of &#34;Headliner&#34; fade into the night, let the melody of love linger in your heart. May the lyrics and sentiments of this song serve as a reminder of the beauty of connection, the power of love, and the enduring harmony that binds us together in the grand symphony of life.', 'music', 'headliner.jpg', '0000-00-00', 'active'),
(37, 3, 'joy', 'Echoes of Resilience: A Journey Through Song', 'Circles - Seventeen&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;In the quiet moments of solitude, where the heart speaks in whispers and the soul seeks solace, the lyrics of &#34;Where am I walking myself?&#34; resonate with a poignant reflection on the path of life. Each verse, each note, is a melody that carries the weight of emotions, painting a portrait of resilience and inner strength.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Navigating the Unknown:&#13;&#10;&#34;Where am I walking myself?&#34; - a question that echoes through the corridors of uncertainty. In the midst of life&#39;s twists and turns, we find ourselves searching for direction, seeking solace in the vast expanse of the unknown.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Silent Cry:&#13;&#10;&#34;When I crying, I go to the skies closer, No one can see my tears,&#34; a poignant reminder of the silent struggles we face. In the solitude of our tears, we find a sanctuary in the skies, a place where emotions can soar freely, unseen by the world.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;The Voice of the Heart:&#13;&#10;&#34;With the voice of our hearts, we passed to each other,&#34; a connection forged through the language of the soul. In moments of voicelessness, it is the heart that speaks volumes, bridging the distance between souls with its unspoken melodies.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Song of Strength:&#13;&#10;&#34;Let&#39;s sing together, To cover the sadness with the powerful song,&#34; a call to arms to find strength in unity and music. The melody becomes a shield against sorrow, a beacon of hope that guides us through the darkest of days.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Embracing Unity:&#13;&#10;&#34;Remember, we are together always, I won&#39;t let go of your hand,&#34; a promise of unwavering support and companionship. In the ebb and flow of life&#39;s journey, we find solace in the knowledge that we are not alone, that our hands are held in unity and love.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;As the echoes of &#34;Where am I walking myself?&#34; fade into the distance, let the melody of resilience linger in your heart. May the lyrics and sentiments of this song serve as a reminder of the strength that lies within, the power of unity, and the enduring melody of hope that guides us through life&#39;s ever-changing symphony.', 'music', 'circles.jpg', '0000-00-00', 'active'),
(38, 4, 'anne01', 'The Flame of Resistance: A Symbol of Inner Strength', 'In the realm of art, a single matchstick with a flickering flame takes center stage, capturing the essence of resistance in its most delicate form. The artwork portrays a profound message, where the flame at the tip symbolizes the unwavering concept of resistance, embodying the inner fortitude and resilience that individuals possess when confronted with life&#39;s challenges.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Metaphor of Strength and Vulnerability:&#13;&#10;At the heart of the artwork lies a powerful metaphor - the flame represents resilience, while the matchstick itself embodies vulnerability and fragility. This juxtaposition highlights the nuanced nature of resistance, showcasing that strength often emerges from moments of vulnerability, and that even the most delicate elements can spark a powerful force.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Embracing the Fire Within:&#13;&#10;The artwork serves as a visual narrative, emphasizing that resistance is not about being impervious to adversity, but rather about embracing the fire within and persevering in the face of obstacles. It conveys the idea that true strength lies in acknowledging one&#39;s vulnerabilities and harnessing them as sources of empowerment.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Igniting Resilience and Growth:&#13;&#10;Just as a small flame can ignite a roaring fire, the artwork symbolizes how even the smallest act of resistance can lead to a cascade of personal growth and triumph. It serves as a poignant reminder that resilience is not about avoiding challenges, but about facing them head-on with courage and determination.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Beacon of Hope and Triumph:&#13;&#10;In its simplicity, the artwork encapsulates a profound truth - that resilience is a transformative force that can lead to triumph and personal evolution. It inspires individuals to kindle the flame of determination within, knowing that even the faintest spark has the power to illuminate the path to resilience, growth, and triumph.&#13;&#10;', 'arts', 'matchsticks.jpg', '0000-00-00', 'active'),
(39, 4, 'anne01', 'Bridging the Divide: The Wealth Gap Through Artistic Lens', 'In the canvas of art, a poignant depiction unfolds - two individuals stand in a rainy setting, each symbolizing a different facet of society&#39;s wealth gap and its profound impact on individual lives. The artwork serves as a visual narrative, shedding light on the stark disparities that exist in our world and the challenges faced by those on opposite ends of the economic spectrum.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Tale of Disparity:&#13;&#10;The scene unfolds with one figure standing under a canopy of umbrellas, a portrayal of the privileged and wealthy individuals who are shielded by layers of protection and support. The umbrellas serve as symbols of financial security, resources, and opportunities that act as barriers against the adversities of life.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Contrast in Fortune:&#13;&#10;In stark contrast, the second figure stands exposed to the elements, devoid of any protective cover. This representation embodies the less fortunate and economically disadvantaged individuals who lack the same access to resources and opportunities. They navigate life&#39;s challenges without the safety net that the privileged enjoy.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Weathering the Storm:&#13;&#10;The rainy environment serves as a backdrop, symbolizing the obstacles and hardships faced by both individuals. It reflects the unequal distribution of wealth and the struggles endured by those who find themselves on the fringes of financial stability. The downpour becomes a metaphor for the societal divide and the harsh realities of economic disparity.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Shining a Light on Inequality:&#13;&#10;Through its evocative imagery, the artwork aims to bring attention to the profound contrast between privilege and adversity, shedding light on the struggles and challenges encountered by the economically disadvantaged. It serves as a visual representation of the wealth gap, urging viewers to reflect on the systemic inequalities that permeate society.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Closing Reflections:&#13;&#10;As we contemplate the imagery before us, let us heed the call to action embedded within the art. May it serve as a catalyst for empathy, understanding, and advocacy, inspiring us to work towards a more equitable and just society where all individuals have access to the same opportunities and support systems, regardless of their economic standing.', 'arts', '2.jpg', '0000-00-00', 'active'),
(40, 4, 'anne01', 'Embracing the Timeless Spirit: A Journey of Self-Reflection Through Art', 'In the realm of art, there exists a masterpiece that transcends time and space, weaving a narrative of self-reflection, the fusion of past and present, and the enduring essence of the human spirit. This artwork serves as a visual symphony, inviting viewers on a contemplative journey of introspection and appreciation for the cyclical nature of life.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Tapestry of Time:&#13;&#10;At the heart of the artwork lies a profound message - the integration of past and present, a harmonious blend of memories and moments that shape our existence. It beckons the viewer to reflect on their life&#39;s journey, to honor the experiences that have sculpted their identity, and to find solace in the interconnectedness of time.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Youthful Essence, Ageless Wisdom:&#13;&#10;As the colors dance on the canvas, the artwork whispers a gentle reminder to embrace one&#39;s inner youth, to nurture the spark of vitality that resides within. It celebrates the wisdom and depth that come with age, urging the viewer to cherish the lessons learned while preserving a connection to the exuberance and curiosity of youth.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;The Eternal Flame of the Human Spirit:&#13;&#10;Through strokes of brilliance and hues of emotion, the artwork captures the timeless nature of the human spirit - resilient, adaptable, and ever-evolving. It serves as a beacon of inspiration, igniting a flame of introspection and growth within each viewer, reminding them of the infinite possibilities that lie within.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;A Call to Reflection:&#13;&#10;As the viewer gazes upon this evocative creation, they are encouraged to pause, to ponder, and to delve into the depths of their own soul. It prompts them to explore the intersections of past and present, to find beauty in the complexities of life&#39;s tapestry, and to embrace the duality of youthfulness and wisdom that resides within.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;In the brushstrokes of this artwork, we find a mirror to our own journey - a reflection of our past, a celebration of our present, and a glimpse into the timeless essence of our being. May it serve as a catalyst for introspection, a reminder of the interconnectedness of life&#39;s chapters, and a tribute to the enduring spirit that guides us through the ever-evolving tapestry of existence.', 'arts', '10.jpg', '0000-00-00', 'active'),
(41, 4, 'anne01', 'Nature is a teacher', 'What happens when you allow everything to be “as it is”?&#13;&#10;A number of years ago I went on holiday to a beautiful part of Portugal. We stayed in a converted farmhouse in the middle of a national park. The farmhouse was in a valley. We arrived in the evening when the birds were just starting to roost. It was still warm and the air smelled sweet with pollen. You could hear the hum of crickets. A small river flowed through that valley. We opened a rickety gate and crossed a small wooden bridge. As we walked along the narrow path that led to our house I had a clear vision of what my morning routine would be like for the next fourteen days. I had been working hard for the last few months and I felt tired. I wanted this holiday to be a mini retreat. I would wake up early each day when it was still quite cool and I would meditate for a while. I imagined myself sitting in a peaceful spot, my mind calm, my body relaxed… listening to the river flowing, hearing the birds and wildlife starting to stir, feeling the first rays of the early morning sun hit my face as it rose over the top of the hill. Present. Even as I write this now, it sounds like paradise to me.&#13;&#10;', 'nature', 'N3.jpg', '0000-00-00', 'active'),
(42, 4, 'anne01', 'Society – The soil in which we grow.', 'In order for any plant to grow and flourish to its full potential, it needs the right conditions.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;The soil is all important. Everything grows in the soil. If the soil is good and you have the right amount of sunshine and water everything takes care of itself. Nature follows its own course. We don’t need to interfere. The tiny acorn grows into the majestic Oak tree.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Would the same Oak tree grow in a desert? Would it flourish in a tiny plant pot? What if the soil is barren and polluted?&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;It is no different for human beings. In order for us to grow and flourish to our full potential, we need the right conditions. In our case, you could think of society as the soil in which we grow. What do I mean when I say “society”? I mean it in the broadest possible sense: our families, our communities, our schools, our friends, our government institutions, our laws, our offices, our work, our recreational spaces, our culture… the world in which we live.&#13;&#10;', 'nature', 'N6.jpg', '0000-00-00', 'active'),
(43, 4, 'anne01', 'The hug of homecoming: Hedonism in the natural world', '“Nature is not a place to visit. It is home.&#13;&#10;– Gary Snyder&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;In a very real sense, mountains and valleys, the seas and the skies, the sun and the earth, the trees and the flowers constitute our home, our natural habitat. Growing up in the modern developed world we can easily come to believe that towns and cities – the urban and artificial environment – is where we naturally belong. But our brains and bodies, which evolved over thousands of years, were designed by and designed for an environment very different to the one we live in now.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;Throughout our evolutionary history we lived in very close connection to the land, with a very close kinship with other creatures. Our physiological system evolved to survive in wild, natural environments and developed a love and kinship for these places that lives on in our DNA.&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10;This connection with the land combined with the kinship we would have felt with other living things that shared the land as their home has hardwired in us a strong sense of the natural world as ‘home’, and the importance of connection with all of life as being essential to our well-being.&#13;&#10;', 'nature', 'N10.jpg', '0000-00-00', 'active'),
